{"tid":729947,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"打手問題&建議改善","createTime":"2018-07-05T04:02:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-05T17:28:18.000Z","uid":13448,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8cf9386eef8eacf4d12560224d71d85cb0fdbead","tid":729947,"uid":13448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T04:02:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lih.kg/729627\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/729627</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/729873\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/729873</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/729111\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/729111</a><br />\n重有其他有就唔po了<br />\n<br />\n每隔幾個鐘開po當無洗板 明知比錢請打手推po <br />\n咁都得？ 唔處理？明知呃人錢揾水魚 hard sell表露無遺<br />\n再者想admin認真諗下係咪真係有必要將同一樣野分咁多個po去不斷開去討論 不斷炒返上黎 明知未1001<br />\n的確如果頻密出po會指為洗板 但admin認為有效處理每6小時以上開po當無洗板既人？<br />\n如admin覺得太難處理 可以考慮下以下方法<br />\nadmin可審視每24小時先可以開1個post設上限既可行性<br />\n好處1 有效地制止為博注意而不斷洗板既煩膠<br />\n其2 由於洗板小 有助集中討<br />\n其3 期望低質po會減少 因為起碼當日開po時 佢知道出完一次低質po後如無人理 嗰日就無Second chances 會諗清楚講乜 同十幾連後都無人理 抵佢沉低啦<br />\n<br />\n壞處 1 對打手會不方便<br />\n其2 開低質po既人轉為攻佔其他po引人注意 有效令用戶block煩膠<br />\n其3 基於低質po 減少 令admin有更多察覺違規po<br />\n其4 出低質po既依然低質 無改變<br />\n<br />\n基本上無咩點變 出低質po既會減小 出高質po既依然會引起討論<br />\n最後制止既都係啲煩膠同打手 有質素既依然會多人睇"},{"pid":"042639aa2884250e41d1e804fc1266d8cb8185e5","tid":729947,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T04:03:58.000Z","msg":"曲線笑緊條友呀"},{"pid":"e25b205a4395de363f1b46c420204103a24dd755","tid":729947,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T04:04:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5efd39141f9b0e636b3d453131108d8a2e0d22f5","tid":729947,"uid":13448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T04:15:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/121342_22c4c0463928b3b8cca7f4967e459395.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F121342_22c4c0463928b3b8cca7f4967e459395.png&h=c5319f32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人討論自然會有人講<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/121343_ad01d1091c2e6690a772dee0a3c301ea.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F121343_ad01d1091c2e6690a772dee0a3c301ea.png&h=2756fb4b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"978196b63f545db6be02ecb2bc5fdece748c32f8","tid":729947,"uid":13448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T04:25:10.000Z","msg":"起碼有開低質po既係隔日一次 只係低質<br />\n只唔係一日幾次 低質兼煩"},{"pid":"bc0ba7cf1a865b52101a480d7c33dfca0231e38b","tid":729947,"uid":13448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T06:15:35.000Z","msg":"所有打手都可以拎吹捧做籍口 可以有萬樣籍口 吹捧淘寶啲貨 唔係sell 連續開po讚同一間餐廳 只係吹捧非打手 <br />\n連登商業性質？<br />\n你要博既 總會揾到籍口<br />\n但事實係 煩膠同打手依然存在"},{"pid":"30587f4f85b47389f1d8f052c4c434a59af118f1","tid":729947,"uid":36084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"042639aa2884250e41d1e804fc1266d8cb8185e5","tid":729947,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T04:03:58.000Z","msg":"曲線笑緊條友呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T06:27:52.000Z","msg":"曲線就可以洗版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0968e724fc22cb77f0a5c481cbcc46fee806ebe0","tid":729947,"uid":36084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T06:30:03.000Z","msg":"條冚家剷之前已經因為洗版ban過7日<br />\n擺明挑機"},{"pid":"cee0b9910343f612acb88674f078ebd8f3f5728e","tid":729947,"uid":36084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T09:37:22.000Z","msg":"又洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45d33567acddd84f4d4262b042fee700c81fc17f","tid":729947,"uid":13448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cee0b9910343f612acb88674f078ebd8f3f5728e","tid":729947,"uid":36084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T09:37:22.000Z","msg":